profile_english:
A serial technopreneur working on Open API & Web technology; IBM Redbooks Thought Leader (2014); Associate trainer in Information Security; Rock Bassist & MusicTech Lover;

Patrick is a serial technopreneur & former IBM Redbooks Thought Leader working in Open API & Open Web technology. After years of exceptional track records in IBM, Patrick started his startup journey and founded beNovelty in order to help business adopting Open API technology and lower the barriers of companies in conducting API business in the era of API Economy.

On top of his startup, Patrick conducted startup coaching & advisory to various sustainable startups from fintech, edutech, traveltech spaces. Starting from 2020, he becomes a technology partner in residency of a Venture Capital helping its early-stage portfolio companies to embrace modern Open API technologies.

